dekho agr aapko shadcn mein customization krni to hr component,box,div ko ek bg color dedo iska use krke aap aaram se customization kr skte

<div className='flex justify-center bg-blue-800 py-10'>
<Carousel className='border w-1/2 bg-cyan-500' >
<CarouselContent style={{padding:'15px'}}>
<CarouselItem className='bg-red-800 text-center' >my item 1</CarouselItem>
<CarouselItem className='bg-red-200 text-center' >my item 2</CarouselItem>
<CarouselItem className='bg-red-500 text-center'  >my item 3</CarouselItem>
</CarouselContent>
<CarouselNext/>
<CarouselPrevious/>

  </Carousel>
</div>
is trh krke aap aaram se customization kr skte and aap hr ek component ko bhut achi trh bna skte 


and aapko hr ek component ko background color deke yeh bhi pta lg jayega ki vo component ka box kha tk hai like agr aapko pta lgana <CarouselContent> ka box kha hai to isko background color deke aapko aaram se pta lg jayega and fir aap ismein customization kr k aaram se aur acha design bna skte 